RT Jay Freeman (saurik)<br>Cydia just joined the legal battle against Apple: "A new lawsuit brought by one of Apple's oldest foes seeks to force the iPhone maker to allow alternatives to the App Store, the latest in a growing number of cases that aim to curb the tech giant's power." <a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/technology/2020/12/10/cydia-apple-lawsuit/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://www.washingtonpost.com/technology/2020/12/10/cydia-apple-lawsuit/</a>